---
title: How Ze Awesome Prussia Game Works
---
flowchart TB
    START["🎮 START SCREEN\nClick START to play!\n(this also turns on sound)"]
    START -->|START| MAIN

    MAIN["🖥️ MAIN SCREEN\nPrussia hangs out with Gilbird\n9 buttons surround him"]

    MAIN --> CLICK["🔘 Click a Button"]
    MAIN --> HOVER["🖱️ Hover Over Prussia\n(or long-press on iPad)"]

    CLICK --> FACE["1. Face changes\n(loads a new SVG image)"]
    FACE --> ANIM["2. Animation plays\n(bounce, shake, sway, etc)"]
    ANIM --> SOUND["3. Sound effect plays\n(mp3 from assets/sounds/)"]
    SOUND --> LABEL["4. Catchphrase appears\n(Kesesese! Dummkopf! etc)"]
    LABEL -->|"2.5 sec timer\n(4 sec for sleep/cry)"| MAIN

    HOVER --> SHOCKED["⚡ Prussia is SHOCKED!\nShake animation + ?! label"]
    SHOCKED -->|"Move mouse away\nor let go"| MAIN

    CLICK ~~~ BTNS

    subgraph BTNS ["The 9 Buttons"]
        direction LR
        B1["😆 Laugh\nbounce"]
        B2["😏 Proud\nsparkle"]
        B3["😤 Angry\nshake"]
        B4["🎵 Sing\nsway"]
        B5["😈 Scheme\npulse"]
        B6["😴 Sleep\nfloat"]
        B7["😢 Cry\ntremble"]
        B8["😳 Embarrass\nshrink"]
        B9["⭐ Awesome\npop"]
    end

    subgraph CODE ["The 3 Code Files"]
        F1["📄 index.html\nScreens + buttons"]
        F2["🎨 style.css\nColors + animations"]
        F3["⚡ app.js\nClick handlers + sound"]
    end

    subgraph CUSTOMART ["🎨 Add Your Own Art"]
        A1["1. Draw an expression"]
